i thought id write in here cause i havent in a while

not much is new school is school nothing changes with that. 

friday i skipped school to hang out with my sis. i wound up going to the galleria so that she could buy the louis vuitton she wanted. its big. she asked "gosh what am i ganna put in this" i said "your other louis". she thought that was funny... who our age has two louis'? shes a crazy girl. im more into coach myself. which is only a teeny bit less. but that was fun its a nice purse of course. then we bought my mom a mothers day present. then we got my sis a dress for today. then i got a smoothie cause i love thirsty's smoothies. and my sis got her fake nails fixed or something. then we left and went to her house to a bit. then we went out with her boyfriend jason to studio movie grill. its an awesome place were u watch a movie while ur eating awesome food i love it. we watched kingdom of heaven which i most definatly loved. its a war/history movie im such a dork. so then we went back to ambers and i stayed the night

we woke up this morning and it was ambers graduation for college. but shes doing her graduate degree next year so shes still got a year left. that took a while but it was ok. then we all went to maggianos and ate a lot of foooood. too much food. then we went back her and sat outside all day and talked it was actually fun. and we didnt have dinner cause lunch was so huge. my sis wore her pretty dress and her new blingin swarovski necklace and bracelet and her new louis. she looked awesome. 

so this has been a good weekend so far. tomorrow we are goin to brunch at lacima in las colinas for mothers day im excited. i love brunch u can eat so much its crazy. alright well im out

this week has been ok i guess. nothing special. i didnt do nething tonite lol. well i mean i didnt go out. i thought i mightve hung out with nick and people but no that ddnt happen. so i called nikki and she was ganna come over and that also never happened... which is cool. i looked thru get well cards that i had from the hospital. u know i got so many cards from family and friends of family its crazy, a lot of people  i didnt even know. but i didnt get one card from a friend. only 2 people came to visit me that were my friends. the rest were family and whatnot. i was happy that so many people cared about me even tho friends didnt show it. i got atleast like 75 cards.  got a card from my guidance councler which i just realized and i thought was sweet, then i got one from the whole fmhs counseling office, i got a card from my church and i got flowers from my church and from my dads work. just like random people its crazy. i had a cute drawing from my young cousins. it took me like an hour to go thru. they were all ina bag witha  balloon i was sent and a medical booklet on ecmo (the machine i was on) to inform people. i have no clue what it really is, there was a picture of me on it they took to show people to get used to before they saw me in person (i guess like there was blood running threw it and i just looked so sick) and i wish we still had that but my mom said she ripped it up cause she didnt want it to be my last picture (just in case things didnt work out). im kinda getting off the subject. lol pretty much i looked thru some hospital memorabilia and it reminded me of those days. thats about all i did tonight cept i slept a lil too. tomorrow im staying home while my parents go to the lake. nick said hed go see the ballad of jack and rose with me in plano (thats the closest place its playing), but i have a feelin that will work out just as well as tonight did lol. o well i have other stuff to do too so itll stll be worth it. thas about it

well not a whole lot has happened. im only updating cause i love kim (as a friend dont worry kim)

easter was good i got bambi and a few other things. but bambi is important. it was a good day i had fun. i love easter.

today was a good day too i went to the doctor at 10:20 and got a shot. then we went home and watched bambi but fell asleep cause we were tired then it was like 12 something and it was warm enough outside and i went outside and tanned till like hmm 3:45? i dunno. it was so hot i jumped in the pool which was FREEZING but it felt sooooo good cause i was so hot. the sun was so hot i dried off within like 2 minutes without a towel or nething. crazy stuff. im sure u all care so much. and then we came in and did just about nothing. and now herre i am

school is tomorrow eeh. not to excited about that bt ill get over it

ok im done

updating cause i think krista mite kill me...

its spring break now nothing completly interesting happened yet. we went to the lake for the weekend and went on the boata lil bit and then came back sunday. then lance came over and we watched some movies. then yesterday i went outside to tan for like 4 hours cause it was so nice out! and then at like 10 at nite i went to see the ring 2 with lance and his friend beatty (sp?). then its today and im just chillin. im way tired and dont really plan on doing nething interesting. whcih is ok cause i just wanna chill i like not doinga whole lot. plus its too windy and not warm enough to go outside to tan. so ya im just ganna sit here and watch step by step. lol i have such a life...

dude im ganna miss my interior design class... i wish it was an 18 week course. britt kim and victoria and i sat at the same table and had a lot of fun. our last two days were spent gettin into trouble... lol im a dork. we played the game trouble and it got pretty intense. britt tends to smash her piece on the pieces she lands on... lol good times. but ya im ganna miss those girls. britt and me would sit at lunch together alone in the corner lol next to the rotc dude... good times but we we wont have the same lunch ne more. me and kim still have us history together but i dont have nething with britt or victoria, so i hope i see em in the hallways. i love u girls im glad i met u all. have fun in ur stupid sat prep class... and food and nutrition??? 

well today was ok. i had babes for lunch which was awesome. very yummy... other than that i sorta wasted the day on the couch sleeping and what not. i slept a lot this weekend which was nice. i also did a page in my scrap book.. yay. good weekend. school tomorrow

so i know i already added today but i have more to say.

today was so fun we left our house at 645 to go to the lakehouse (i slept on the way up). we got here at about nine and my parents went to get our jet ski unwinterized or something like that. then they got lunch/breakfast from pantera bread which was cool i never ate there they got me this awesome peanut butter and jelly and this awesome cinammon bagel bites stuff. i love food. so i had the bagel bites for breakfast then me and my mom watched casablanca while my dad picked up the jet ski. then he got home and we went out on the boat. it was lots of fun we stayed out for three to four hours im not sure. it was sorta windy at some points but when it wasnt it was great. im a lil bit sunburnt which is sorta a nice change from being white lol... well ya know it feels less like winter which i like. and i ate the amazing peanut butter and jelly out on the boat and then we eventually came back finished casablanca and then i ate a hamburger outside while we looked at the lake and my parents had margaritas. it was such a typical summer day i loved it... too bad its winter???? lol... i liked it.. ugh and tomorrow i come back and life goes back to normal. which is ok. and then monday i have school which im not looking forward to. even tho i get to wear my purse... YAY. rite now my parents are out to eat. and i am watching tv and just chillin. my face is like burning hot cause its a lil red. its not that bad i dont think. we'll see tho i havent really looked in the mirror. i hope spring break is nice i wanna go out on the boat some more. we arent goin ne where special we will prolly go up to the lake a lil. we were thinkin bout a cruise but silly school decided to put easter and spring break together and we have to be here for easter ccause my sis has a different spring break. well thats about it

so yesterday was a very very awesome day

i went to school and took exams which sucked but the half day made up for it. i fell asleep from 12:30 to 3:30 which was very very nice. then my mom came home and we went to frisco mall to get possibly the cutest purse ever.
http://www.coach.com/shop/product_nobefree.asp?product_no=6717&category_id=416
thats it except its in green. it made me happy and then i got shoes to match it. then after all that i went home and went to lances. we watched frailty somewhat. its a good movie. good times.

well thats about it for yesterday. the rest of the week was eh. o cept thursday was my moms birthday and we went to cafe italia (well now its called italian bistro). the dude gave us free desert cause my parents go there a lot. and ya that was fun i baked her a cake which was not as good as i wanted it to be but it was still pretty good i guess.

right now im at the lake house its sposed to be 86 degrees today so im thinkin im goin on the boat YAY. not warm enough to actually go in tho but itll be fun.

soo ya ive been a lil bit confused lately. i just wish that i knew what was goin on cause i definatly dont have a clue. but id love for someone to clue me in. thatd be great. i dont like wondering! i get major mixed signals

its been a good week!

wednesday lance came over and we watched one flew over the cuckoos nest which was amazing but ive seen it before but it was still amazing. it was fun

thursday we had a feild trip for interior design which was also fuN! mrs. bell is a lot of fun we went out to eat and stuff it was great it took up most of the day. then i had guitar which was ok i didnt do especially great. but ya it was a fun day.

friday kelli got grounded :(. but i hung out with lance which was a lot of fun!!!! ya we watched a movie lol (surprise). we watched the shining which also has jack nicholson who is great. ya that was great fun.

and right now lance just left. we watched the terminal and we played play station 2 gran turismo... he got me some liscences cause i only had one. ya i spend a lot of time with lance for my standards since i dont usually go out that much. but hes really fun and i like it. and id hang out with him even more if it was possible. hes a very cool guy. 

ya thats just about it
ugh last nite kinda wasnt cool at all... well i went to a party and it was fun but ya... some uncool stuff happened

so this week was somewhat cool but then parts of it sucked

tuesday i had to do these notecards for english that took about an hour or more. 

wednesday i went to lances house and we watched 21 grams. its a really awesome movie. i had fun hes a fun guy.

thursday i worked my butt off so that i could do the stupid rough draft that we had 2 days to do. i didnt work on it the first day cause i thought itd be quick but it most definatly wasnt. i had to cancelmy guitar lessons cause i knew itd take forever and i didnt really feel good. so i started at about 5:30 after i ate dinner and stuff... then, with the tv off almost the whole nite, i finished at about 11:15. it was the longest paper ive ever had to do in the shortest amount of time. it was crazy but its over with and it doesnt really matter all that much. 

friday i went to the movies with lance joe and nick. it was a lot of fun. we saw hitch... but funny story behind that. we bought tickets and were in the movie already for constantine, and a cop comes in and is all like im ganna need to see ur tickets and ids please, theres been a complaint that there are some under aged kids in here. and first of all 3 of us were of age, second we werent really doing nething wrong. like we werent being loud or nething. so basically lance didnt have an id which is ok so we went an saw hitch. but hitch was a really good movie i laughed a lot. 

and thats about my weekend so far cause its still like 10:30 in the morning on saturday.

so i had a fun weekend. friday me kelli and lance went to chickfila... lance is a cool guy even tho he didnt have fun. then me and kelli met chris up at the mall. and then me and kelli went to my place and had a sleep over and watched the notebook. lol but i guess we were both really tired cause we fell asleep like at 11 lol. my mom made waffles for us in the morning then kelli had to go cause her parents wanted to look for cars with her. but surprise they already got her a car and its a black mustang which is awesome for her and im so happy for her. then later that day me and my mom went to stonebriar and i tried on a lot of clothes but nothing really fit except i got this really cute jacket from rampage. a lot of the stuff that did fit was dry clean only which is stupid. but the jacket is cute so its all worth it. and then today i stayed home. i had homework and stuff so i did that. it was really nice out so i didnt get as much as i wanted done cause i have a research project ugh. and now im watchin desperate housewives and thats about it

so lent is tomorrow and im catholic. i decided to give up gangs of new york. YIKES. this means i cant watch the movie... look at the movie book... im ganna take off all the backgrounds and stuff on my computer which is the reason for my lack of an icon. i cant speak the words daniel day-lewis or gangs of new york. it could actually be pretty tough. its ganna be hard. if u know me at all u know itll be hard. it also means i cant look it up on the internet on ebay or look it up on random websites. the only thing ill have is my poster hanging up... which i cant take down cause its too expensive to give up. ill just try to ignore it a lil bit. well im ganna go i just thought id let you all know whats goin on

ugh...

things dont always go ur way i guess. so i guess the eagles didnt win. 24 to 21. that is so stupid. so close. we were so close!!!!! i cant beleive it. ill prolly be upset all tonite... maybe some of tomorrow too. and then ill just be spiteful for a while. but it was a good game. we really did good in the begining and it looked like the patriots didnt have a chance... but then i dunno what happened. its an unfortunate thing. but im glad we got this far. and after this stupid speech from the patriots on their stupid cheap win... the simpsons comes on which looks like itll be funny. the simpsons have the ability to chear me up. i definatly ate a lot while i was watching the game. my throat really hurts from screaming at the tv the whole time and i think i might loose my voice. but u know what..? its worth it. we had some awesome plays. i got pretty excited and maybe even jumped out of my chair a few times... which is pretty impressive... i cant say that i do that for any other show. and i watch a lot of tv. the eagles deserved it. thats all i have to say. and for all of my friends that have rooted against me just cause i love the eagles... u got ur wish. but i dont really care what people think. the eagles deserved it and thats what matters.

so on another note... its been a good week i guess. i forget what day but we got our schedules this week for next year. im plannin on doin senior out both semesters. i dont have much i need done and i definatly dont want to graduate early. i dont wanna miss out of my last semester of high school... thats when all the important things happen!!!

i got my hair cut. hopefully u cant tell. i got it cut as lil as possible just cause i had to cause its been a while... but i didnt want it any shorter cause i am still growin it out. 

my sis came over from wednesday to saturday. that was pretty cool. and she had her doggy jaike. on friday i took off school and me and my sis hung out all day. i had fun. i like it when she comes over.

well thats about it. i wrote a lot today. 
love manda

ugh im really mad at a certain someone. i am sick of her. shes a huge liar. w/e ive had it... i found out yet another reason not to like her. but dont even ask me what it is cause im not ganna tell u.
liars are nto cool

ummmm friday was interesting... i dunno. i dont wanna talk about friday.

and then today is pretty good like saturday. its a pretty chill day. no eagles game. but next week will for sure make up for that. my sis will be coming over with her doggy soon. i just got finished doing some scrapbooking with my mom. its a fun thing to do. we are making a christmas one... i know it seems a lil late but we are using pics from this year and stuff...

ya so this weekend has been bad and good... mostly bad.

well ill get over it
love manda

and then today well i already told u bout the game. and my sister is visitign which is cool! and tomorrow i have no school so ya im happy bout that.
